track_notes: Hike along the Appalachian Trail.  Parking is available at Dicks Creek Gap.

Alternate route from Blue Ridge Gap along Charlies Creek Road.  2.7 miles along the Appalachian Trail with 1200 EG.  Road is rough and may not be accessible by low clearance vehicles.  The section of road north of Blue Ridge Gap is always rougher and high-clearance and 4WD is required.  I elected to not drive this section and hiked and additional 1.7 miles/465 EG from the confluence of Charlies and Flat Branch Creeks (34.958, -83.571).
track_title: W4G/NG-021 Buzzard Knob from Blue Ridge Gap

track_notes: Hike along the AT from Dick Creek Gap with an off trail turn at coordinates N34.93354 W83.60215 to get into the AZ.  3.1 mile hike with 1600 feet of EG.  On the return - activate Little Bald Knob W4G/NG-032.
